---
title: Spicy Peruvian Aji Verde Chicken Bowls Note: Blender required
description: The star of this colorful dish is creamy, herbaceous ají verde sauce, a bright Peruvian sauce made with cilantro, garlic, and lime juice puréed in the blender. You’ll spoon over juicy roasted chicken cutlets atop roasted sweet potatoes and refried black beans. A squeeze of lime and sprinkle of chili flakes deliver a final kick of tang and heat.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/669eb8a3f2f831ddecf680f0-4fb4276e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/669eb8a3f2f831ddecf680f0-en-US.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
